s = int(input())
while s:
    k = int(input())
    l1 = list(map(int, input().split()))
    l2 = list(map(int, input().split()))
    l1.remove(max(l1))
    l2.remove(max(l2))
    o = sum(l1)
    p = sum(l2)
    if o == p:
        print('Draw')
    elif p == min(o, p):
        print('Bob')
    elif o == min(o, p):
        print('Alice')
    s = s - 1

for i in range(int(input())):
    N = int(input())
    A = list(map(int, input().split()))
    B = list(map(int, input().split()))
    A.sort()
    B.sort()
    total_alice = 0
    total_bob = 0
    i = 0
    while i < N:
        total_alice = total_alice + A[i]
        total_bob = total_bob + B[i]
        i = i + 1
    a = total_alice - A[N - 1]
    b = total_bob - B[N - 1]
    if a < b:
        print('Alice')
    elif a > b:
        print('Bob')
    else:
        print('Draw')
